msgstr "Non toccate nulla!"

#. [message]: speaker=Aerius
#: wesnoth-To_Lands_Unknown/scenarios/02_Central_Palace.cfg:233
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "What amazing workmanship. I don’t understand how you were able to entrap "
