#: wesnoth-To_Lands_Unknown/scenarios/12_Siege_of_Mag-Magar.cfg:610
#: wesnoth-To_Lands_Unknown/scenarios/17_Siege_of_Kharos.cfg:553
#: wesnoth-To_Lands_Unknown/scenarios/17_Siege_of_Kharos.cfg:1225
