#: wesnoth-To_Lands_Unknown/scenarios/13_A_New_Leader.cfg:183
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Please, don’t! I beg you! If you tell her, she will rip my throat out!"
msgid ""
"Please, I beg you, anything but that! She will rip my throat out if she "
"finds out!"
msgstr ""
"Vi prego, non fatelo! Vi prego! Se le dite questo, mi taglierà la gola!"

#. [message]: speaker=Malib
#: wesnoth-To_Lands_Unknown/scenarios/13_A_New_Leader.cfg:187
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "So we have come to an understanding. I knew I could count on you. Bye!"
